# macOS
.DS_Store

# Security - DO NOT TRACK (sensitive/personal data)
.specstory/
memory-bank/private/
# memory-bank/shared/ IS tracked — it holds project scaffolding
# (projectbrief.md, productContext.md, etc.) that dev-kid + the
# post-checkout hook depend on. The .constitution.md symlink under
# shared/ is generated by the hook on each checkout, so ignore it.
memory-bank/shared/.constitution.md
CLAUDE.md
.claude/
# Defense-in-depth: explicit ignore for the Claude Code agent
# worktree dir so a future narrowing of `.claude/` (e.g. tracking
# .claude/skills/) cannot accidentally commit sibling worktrees.
/.claude/worktrees/

# Temp files - DO NOT TRACK
CLAUDE_SKILLS_CHEATSHEET.md
DOCUMENTATION_REVIEW_SUMMARY.md

